file.name: input.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  /user:
    get:
      tags:
        - user
      summary: Get user
      description: This can only be done by the logged in user.
      operationId: getUser
      responses:
        default:
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token.Id'
components:
  schemas:
    Token.Id:
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 10
    User:
      x-swagger-router-model: io.swagger.petstore.model.User
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 10
        username:
          type: string
          example: theUser
        firstName:
          type: string
          example: John
        lastName:
          type: string
          example: James
        email:
          type: string
          example: john@email.com
        password:
          type: string
          example: 12345
        phone:
          type: string
          example: 12345
        userStatus:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          example: 1
          description: User Status
      xml:
        name: user
      type: object
  parameters:
    username:
      name: username
      in: path
      description: name that need to be deleted
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
